title: 820-3115-b
message: Fans rotate at full speed and it is also very slow to enter the system, apple service diagnostic report Th1H Fin Stack Proximity Sensor Reads Within Operating Range

title: 820-3115-b
message: If no other error when continuing on error, Q5520.

title: 820-3115-b
message:
